About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalalâ€™s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Click here to watch full episodes of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSXTaG1fT0cTXtajBo1G2UEa_wE8BVSU7

snippet.title: TRUMP v2.0 | Standup Comedy by Rahul Dua | 2025
snippet.description:
Move over IPL 2.0, here is Trump 2.0.
I travelled to USA and Canada in Feb-Mar 2025 for my standup comedy tour with my new special (btw, India tour is on and I am coming to Australia and New Zealand, so you can get the tickets here: https://linktr.ee/therahulduatour).
This video has jokes about my time and my observations there, based on true events: USA vs Canada, Trump and Elon Musk, missed flights, the tip culture and more. Wrote, rehearsed and recorded all within a month of travel, so pls give it a watch and let me know you favourite joke in the comments below. 
Pls drop a like, it really helps the video. and share it with your friends and family members who are in USA or are planning to visit. 

#standupcomedy #trump #usavscanada 

Shot at The Regent Theatre, Boston, MA on 29th March 2025
Shot by: Prathmesh Mohite (@shutterversebypm)
Edited by: Gaurav Bhatt (@gauravbhatt101)
Audio Mix and Master: Yash Rajiv Barse (@yashrajivbarse)
Tour slates' design: Ripudaman Pandey (@ripudaman_pandey)
Thumbnail design: Hritik Singh (@Ritzdesigns_)
On ground production: Mehtab Singh (@mehtabolism__)
Subtitles: Man Dream Production (@mandreamproduction)

Special Thanks: Sourav Bangotra, Anubhav Singh Bassi

snippet.description:
Exploring Death Valley National Park â€“ Chapter 1

Come with me on an epic one-day road trip from Las Vegas to Death Valley National Park, one of the hottest and most extreme places on Earth! â˜€ï¸ğŸ”¥

We started our journey early from Las Vegas, stopped for a relaxing breakfast, and stumbled upon a charming antique street shop along the way. With desert vibes kicking in, we finally reached the Death Valley National Park signâ€”and the excitement was real!

After grabbing our park pass, our first stop was the iconic Zabriskie Point â€“ a breathtaking view of golden badlands shaped over millions of years. From there, we explored the unique and otherworldly wonders of Death Valley:

ğŸ§­ Stops in this vlog:
 â€¢ Zabriskie Point â€“ stunning views and badland formations.
 â€¢ Furnace Creek â€“ the heart of the valley and home to historic sites.
 â€¢ Badwater Basin â€“ the lowest point in North America at 282 feet below sea level!
 â€¢ Devilâ€™s Golf Course â€“ jagged salt flats you can hear cracking beneath your feet.
 â€¢ Artistâ€™s Palette â€“ colorful hills formed by oxidized minerals.
 â€¢ Shoshone Village â€“ a peaceful desert town with natural springs and history.

In this vlog, I also share fascinating scientific facts, geological insights, and historical stories that reveal the true wonder of Death Valley.

We wrapped up the day by heading back to Las Vegas, with hearts full and cameras packed with memories!

ğŸ¥ Perfect for science lovers, nature explorers, and road trip fans!

snippet.title: Superman | Official Trailer | DC
snippet.description:
Your choices, your actions, thatâ€™s what makes you who you are. #Superman - Only In Theaters and @Imax July 11

â€œSuperman,â€ DC Studiosâ€™ first feature film to hit the big screen, is set to soar into theaters worldwide this summer from Warner Bros. Pictures.  In his signature style, James Gunn takes on the original superhero in the newly imagined DC universe with a singular blend of epic action, humor and heart, delivering a Superman whoâ€™s driven by compassion and an inherent belief in the goodness of humankind. 

DC Studios heads Peter Safran and Gunn are producing the film, which Gunn directs from his own screenplay, based on characters from DC, Superman created by Jerry Siegel and Joe Shuster.

The film stars David Corenswet (â€œTwisters,â€ â€œHollywoodâ€) in the dual role of Superman/Clark Kent, Rachel Brosnahan (â€œThe Marvelous Mrs. Maiselâ€) as Lois Lane and Nicholas Hoult (the â€œX-Menâ€ movies, â€œJuror #2â€) as Lex Luthor.  The film also stars Edi Gathegi (â€œFor All Mankindâ€), Anthony Carrigan (â€œBarry,â€ â€œGothamâ€), Nathan Fillion (the â€œGuardians of the Galaxyâ€ films, â€œThe Suicide Squadâ€), Isabela Merced (â€œAlien Romulusâ€), Skyler Gisondo (â€œLicorice Pizza,â€ â€œBooksmartâ€), Sara Sampaio (â€œAt Midnightâ€), MarÃ­a Gabriela de FarÃ­a (â€œThe Moodysâ€), Wendell Pierce (â€œSelma,â€ â€œTom Clancyâ€™s Jack Ryanâ€), Alan Tudyk (â€œAndorâ€), Pruitt Taylor Vince (â€œBird Boxâ€) and Neva Howell (â€œGreedy Peopleâ€).

â€œSupermanâ€ is executive produced by Nikolas Korda, Chantal Nong Vo and Lars Winther.  Behind the camera, Gunn is joined by frequent collaborators, including director of photography Henry Braham, production designer Beth Mickle, costume designer Judianna Makovsky and composer John Murphy, along with composer David Fleming (â€œThe Last of Usâ€) and editors William Hoy (â€œThe Batmanâ€) and Craig Alpert (â€œDeadpool 2,â€ â€œBlue Beetleâ€).  

DC Studios Presents a Troll Court Entertainment/The Safran Company Production, A James Gunn Film, â€œSuperman,â€ which will be in theaters and IMAXÂ® nationwide on July 11, 2025, and internationally beginning 9 July 2025, distributed by Warner Bros. Pictures.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu)

Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer

Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder Suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi

snippet.title: chann se jo toota mera sapna
snippet.description:
A couple of months ago I had promised myself that I will take up YouTube more seriously. Creating content in the last seven years has been really fulfilling. Par YT par kabhi regularly aur shiddat se content nahi banaya. As a professional yapper, I realised I have a lot more to say, write, share and perform. Aur kahin se toh shuru karna hee padega. 

So, with the resolve that har saturday ek nayi video (hey mata rani, please saath dijiye), I am so happy to share this. Bahut zyada he honest video hai. Enjoy please.

Follow me on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/kushakapila?igsh=MTJscmJ5aXFxeTZobQ%3D%3D&utm_source=qr

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalalâ€™s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

snippet.title: Churake - Vilen X Kanika Kapoor (Official Video)
snippet.description:
â€˜Churake' is a song about a cosmopolitan city girl who falls for a traditional desi guy. As she tries to express her feelings, he consistently pushes her away, burdened by family responsibilities and hesitant to get entangled in a complicated romance. All of this is happening in a delightful, coming-of-age manner.

Artist : Vilen, Kanika Kapoor
Lyrcist : Vilen
Composer : Vilen
Music : Vilen, Gaurav Pahuja
Director : Vilen
Female lead : Sakshi Sobhya
Screenplay : Vilen
Editor : Vilen
DOP : Alex
Color Correction : Vilen
Make up Artist : Dinky Magoo
Mix Master : Hanish Taneja
Music programming : Maniac
Recording studio : G10 Studio, Yash Raj Studios
Curation Partner : Rtist91
Casting : Amit Om Malik

Label : Darks Music Company

Lyrics -

Ankhiyan milake na baaeri tu
Battiyan bujha ke na ja na

Ratiyan jagake bhi tu
mere samne na ra

Sakhiyan chidaein pal pal
Meri saans chadhake na ja na

Ratiyan jagake bhi tu
Mere samne na ra


Na chaal sharabi dekhunga
Na baat nawabi phekunga

Simple saada su chora
Tere haath main aaun na

Tu kyu itraave re chori
Tanne aankh bhi tha ke dekhun na

Manne saaf rehne de
Mann mai mere meil chadhave na

Manne kaam bade se karne
Mere kandhe pe bojh do baatan ka

Sada izzat se karvaani
Kade naak kataani na

Battiyan bujha ke na ja na

Ratiyan jagake bhi tu
mere samne na ra

Sakhiyan chidaein pal pal
Meri saans chadhake na ja na

Ratiyan jagake bhi tu
Mere samne na ra


Tellyphone laga lena
Tu teri diwani ko

Mai jaan nahi mangu
Banjau teri kahani jo

Manne time nahi chori
Deewani baton ka

Na ashik mai na karna
Koe showk kharabi ka

Ho jaungi teri tu tera rang chadha dena
Dhal jaungi tujhsi jeene ka dhang bta dena

Main tuta hoya gilaas su
Mujhmai jaam bhare kyu khamekha

Sab bikhra bikhra handega
Fer naam lagaiye na

snippet.title: Dieting | Saunkan Saunkanay 2 |Ammy Virk, Sargun Mehta, Nimrat Khaira |Miss Pooja |Desi Crew |D Harp
snippet.description:
Get ready to groove to "Dieting", the upbeat new track from Saunkan Saunkanay 2! Sung by Nimrat Khaira and Miss Pooja, with Music Directed by Desi Crew and Music Composed and lyrics by D Harp, this fun number adds a playful twist to dieting. Starring Ammy Virk, Sargun Mehta, and Nimrat Khaira, the film promises full-on Punjabi entertainment!

Movie Releasing in Theaters on 30th May 2025
